<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10111316>
    dc:description "FIG. 12. — A-F, Palliolatella robusta n. sp., le Piziou TP 83 4; A, holotype; B-F, paratypes; G-J, Seguenzaella miocenica n. gen. n. sp., le Piziou T’P 83 2; G-I, holotype; J, paratype; K, L, Buliminella arcuata n. sp., holotype, le Mincé TM 83 3; M-Q, Bisaccioides tonnetoi n. sp., le Piziou TP 83 1; M, paratype; N, test brisé montrant la structure des plaques recouvrant l’ouverture et les sutures; O-Q, holotype. Échelles: A-L, N, 100 μm; M, O-Q, 200 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10111316/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

